text: @RealJamesWoods POTUS Pelosi would make the April Coronavirus peak seem like “the good old days!”  I think of it every time I see POTUS Trump and VPOTUS Pence together at an event. Hope that, like pilots and co-pilots, they don’t eat the same entree.
